msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/matrix-multiply-accelerators.md:266
msgid "CG2 and CG1 (standard) must not be mixed in the same kernel."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../advanced/matrix-multiply-accelerators.md:269
msgid ""
"tcgen05 is only available on **Blackwell datacenter** GPUs (SM 100a). "
"Consumer Blackwell (SM 120) uses the older `mma.sync` instruction set. Check "
"the target architecture before reaching for the tcgen05 API."
